Symbol.Script_3D:
!! Design Table 04.gsm
IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
nos=abs(nos) bss=abs(bss) deth=abs(deth) tsh=abs(tsh)
define material "builtInMatBlackPlastic" 0, 0.333333, 0.313725, 0.294118, 0.15, 0.15, 0.45, 0, 5, 0, 0.784314, 0.784314, 0.784314, 0, 0, 0, 0
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN END IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN gs_resol = 4
MATERIAL cvmat a1=a-nos*2 b1=b-nos*2 ADD nos,nos,bss a0=a1 b0=b1 GOSUB 10 ADDZ zzyzx-bss-tsh-deth GOSUB 10 DEL 1 ADD deth,0,deth ROTY -90 a0=zzyzx-bss-tsh-deth*2 GOSUB 10 ADDZ deth-a1 GOSUB 10 DEL 2 ADDY (b1-deth)/2 BLOCK a1-deth*2,deth,a0 DEL 1 FOR xx=1 TO numc-1 ADD (a1-deth)/numc*xx-deth,deth,0 BLOCK deth,(b1-deth)/2-deth,a0 ADDY (b1-deth)/2 BLOCK deth,(b1-deth)/2-deth,a0 DEL 2 NEXT xx DEL 2
ADD nos+deth*2,nos+deth*2,zzyzx-tsh MATERIAL gs_leg_mat RESOL gs_resol CYLIND tsh-deth/2,deth*0.75 ADDX a1-deth*4 CYLIND tsh-deth/2,deth*0.75 ADDY b1-deth*4 CYLIND tsh-deth/2,deth*0.75 ADDX deth*4-a1 CYLIND tsh-deth/2,deth*0.75 DEL 4
MATERIAL gs_top_mat RESOL 2*gs_resol ADDZ zzyzx-deth/2 BLOCK a,b,deth/2 DEL 1 ADD nos+deth*2,nos+deth*2,bss GOSUB 20 addx a1-deth*4 GOSUB 20 addy b1-deth*4 GOSUB 20 addx deth*4-a1 GOSUB 20 DEL 4 END
10: CPRISM_ cvmat,cvmat,trmat,5,deth,0,0,15,a0,0,15, a0,b0,15,0,b0,15,0,0,-1 RETURN
20:
ROTZ rnd(360) ADD -deth/2,-deth*2,0
MATERIAL gs_leg_mat RECT deth,deth*3
ROTY 90 POLY 4,0,0,0,deth*3,bss*0.65,deth*3,bss*0.65,deth*2 ADDZ deth POLY 4,0,0,0,deth*3,bss*0.65,deth*3,bss*0.65,deth*2 DEL 3
ADDZ -bss*0.6 ROTY 90 ADDZ -deth*0.3 MATERIAL "builtInMatBlackPlastic" CYLIND deth*0.6,bss*0.3 ADDZ -deth*0.1
MATERIAL gs_leg_mat PRISM_ 4,deth*0.8,0,0,979,bss*0.4,360,4079, 0,0,979,bss*0.3,360,4079
DEL 5 RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
HOTSPOT2 a/2,b/2,0 call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 4, unID = 3000 unID = 1
PEN gs_cont_pen POLY2_ 4,5,0,0,1,a,0,1,a,b,1,0,b,1
HOTSPOT2 a/2,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 0,b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2,b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a,b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, b, 1, 0, b, 1, 0, 0, -1
HOTLINE2 0,0,A,0 HOTLINE2 A,0,A,B HOTLINE2 A,B,0,B HOTLINE2 0,B,0,0
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
!!! ******************************** Minimal Space VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSSide" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSRear" RANGE [0,)
values "numc" range (0, int((A - 2 * nos - 2 * deth) / (2 * deth))]
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
Symbol.Comment: Стол с дополнительными шкафчиками и минимальным пространством.
